data.description: COUNTRY CHARM CLOSE TO TOWN! This gorgeous home sits on a beautiful 15 acres of pine trees and pasture, with a variety of wildlife. Outside you will find 2 large out buildings, 1 storage shed, and loafing sheds. There is a water well used for outside watering. Inside the home offers plenty of room to entertain friends and family. Living area with vaulted ceilings and fireplace, large kitchen, and an amazing large master bedroom. All of this just minutes from town where you will find plenty of places to shop and eat. If you are looking for the convenience of being close to town, but want the seclusion county life offers then this home is for you! New roof installed January 2024!
